### 10.1 CSS Custom Properties for Dark Mode

```css
:root {
  --surface-primary: #ffffff;
  --surface-secondary: #f5f5f5;
  --text-primary: #1a1a1a;
  --text-secondary: #666666;
  --border-subtle: #e0e0e0;
