## 13. Summary & Action Items

### Best Practices Checklist

**Card Design**
- [ ] Use semantic HTML (`<article>`, `<h2>` headings)
- [ ] Ensure entire card is clickable with pseudo-element
- [ ] Implement keyboard focus states (outline, underline)
