## 9. PERFORMANCE OPTIMIZATION

### 9.1 GPU Acceleration

**Best Practices:**

```css
/* Enable GPU acceleration with transform and opacity */
.gpu-accelerated {
  will-change: transform, opacity;
  transform: translate3d(0, 0, 0); /* Force GPU */
}

/* Use for animations */
